== Format drive ==

=== BIOS/MBR ===

Create three partitions. 128MB for {{Path|/boot}}, 1024MB for swap, and the rest for {{Path|/}}

{{RootCmd|cfdisk /dev/sda}}

Format the partitions:

{{RootCmd
|mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda1
|mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3
|mkswap /dev/sda2 && swapon /dev/sda2
}}

