== Mount partitions ==

=== BIOS/MBR ===

{{RootCmd
|mkdir -p /mnt/gentoo
|mount /dev/sda3 /mnt/gentoo
|mkdir /mnt/gentoo/boot
|mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/gentoo/boot
}}

=== BIOS/GPT ===

{{RootCmd
|mkdir -p /mnt/gentoo
|mount /dev/sda4 /mnt/gentoo
|mkdir /mnt/gentoo/boot
|mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/gentoo/boot
}}

=== UEFI/GPT ===

{{RootCmd
|mkdir -p /mnt/gentoo
|mount /dev/sda4 /mnt/gentoo
|mkdir /mnt/gentoo/boot
|mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/gentoo/boot
